{"tid":827733,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【迪士尼網劇】Marvel英雄獨立開劇 洛基同紅女巫都有份","createTime":"2018-09-19T06:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T15:29:39.000Z","uid":119223,"like":93,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ab8969a808aad8e70a76779cf67b921fa17790d6","tid":827733,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:59:10.000Z","msg":"於《復仇者3》中，邪神洛基慘死犧牲，但佢終於有機會「翻生」！有報導指，迪士尼打算為一班英雄開獨立作，變成迷你劇集，並將於其自家串流電視獨家播出。<br />\n<br />\n有見及串流電視Netflix賺大錢，最近迪士尼都積極籌備緊自家串流電視，當中除咗有過往嘅Marvel電影睇之外，最新消息係將打算為Marvel英雄開獨立作，而最大機會嘅就係推出洛基同紅女巫嘅迷你劇，<span style=\"color: red;\">而且分別會由湯赫度斯頓（Tom Hiddleston）及伊莉莎伯奧遜（Elizabeth Olsen）演返劇中角色，唔會易角。</span>預計拍攝預算方面，可以同電影製作媲美。迷你劇每齣大約有6至8集，而Marvel主席兼監製Kevin Feige更會親身主理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180919/large/1537338113_7da0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180919%2Flarge%2F1537338113_7da0.jpg&h=36460e7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fe98b5d789554e27c188a144299ac70e9c8aa96","tid":827733,"uid":119223,"like":21,"dislike":8,"score":13,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"乜個啲英雄劇唔係好鍾意搞平行世界 一個角色唔同人演架咩 ?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b68d74ea7d62037f47b544c489cf9faf28bf625","tid":827733,"uid":99364,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d7fae642d68ffcc57397518c672556a456c5c0e","tid":827733,"uid":141210,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"3fe98b5d789554e27c188a144299ac70e9c8aa96","tid":827733,"uid":119223,"like":21,"dislike":8,"score":13,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"乜個啲英雄劇唔係好鍾意搞平行世界 一個角色唔同人演架咩 ?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:04:21.000Z","msg":"你有冇睇過架<br />\nnetflix好多marvel影集都會抽avengers水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <